Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oke!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi, Ketua.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi, kau dekat dengan Mizuha, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nama Mizuha tak ada di daftar kelas.
