Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah mengamati rumah mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya tak ada tanda mereka pindah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah. Kalau begitu, dia pasti masih…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Besok ulang tahun Mizuha, 'kan?
