Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.21,0:08:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi tak apa selama dia tahu\Nbanyak orang yang mencemaskannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.66,0:08:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski bertemu,\Nkami tak tahu harus bilang apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika salah langkah,\Nrasanya semua akan berakhir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.55,0:08:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari berpikir lebih sederhana.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ketua Hanna,\Nkau ingin bertemu Mizuha lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.32,0:08:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa dia tak akan datang hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.95,0:09:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi mari tetap ke rumahnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga buatkan hadiah ulang tahun…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.29,0:09:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian taruh ini
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}di kotak surat kami, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau ayah Mizuha?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu hadiah ulang tahun Mizuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, tapi Mizuha mungkin\Nakan menolaknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagi putriku,\Nini masa lalu yang sudah dibuang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak ada jalan kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.35,0:09:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dan dia tak berniat begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian mau pindah ke mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.39,0:09:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tempat yang tak bisa kalian jangkau.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan pergi dengan putriku besok.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sangat jauh hingga kalian\Ntak bisa pura-pura berteman lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.65,0:09:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuharap kalian mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.95,0:09:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya percuma pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia baik sekali sudah mengembalikannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada yang terjatuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku yakin sudah menempelnya dengan erat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.88,0:09:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aneh sekali. Apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Keluargaku tercinta".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Tercinta"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tetap harus ke rumah Mizuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah tak ada cara\Nuntuk membalikkan keadaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya akan menyusahkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh ya, aku belum nyatakan\Nperasaanku kepada Mizuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus memberitahunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sebabnya aku juga ikut!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kesempatan terakhirku!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aoki, kau harus pergi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.53,0:10:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nyatakanlah, Wakil Ketua.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mendukungmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, ayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamu hari ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.84,0:10:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Bon dari Yayasan Persik Lezat,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pakar masalah penyiangan di Renril.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.38,0:10:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo, Semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.30,0:10:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Pak Bon tampil di TV lagi.\N- Pekan lalu,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.13,0:10:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Ini siaran langsung.\N- Aliansi Pencabut Tanaman Internasional
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Dia selebritas.\N- menundanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kakek, bantu aku bicara dengan Pak Bon.\N- Menurutmu terjadi sesuatu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Minta dia lakukan tugas kebersihannya.\N- Itu pasti karena protes keras
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.18,0:10:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kepala Sekolah marah besar.\N- kelompok pencinta lingkungan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku berangkat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.69,0:10:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tonari, bantu aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kutinggalkan tubuh tiruanku\Ndi ruang petugas kebersihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.99,0:11:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisakah kau memeriksanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa aku?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.49,0:11:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak masuk hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena aku akan menyatakan cinta\Nkepada Mizuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.41,0:11:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kesempatan terakhirku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan membantunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.46,0:11:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mengerti, 'kan?\NIni hari yang sangat penting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.55,0:11:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi, ayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mana kutahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.90,0:11:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang kembali, Fushi. Bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mobil itu menuju\Narea rumah kakek Mizuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa ke bawah tanah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin ada hubungannya dengan tempat\Nyang dikunjungi Fen dan Nixon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Klub Riset Hal Gaib akhirnya pergi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ke markas musuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.59,0:11:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, Klub Riset Hal Gaib! Semangat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.50,0:11:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Klub Riset Hal Gaib! Semangat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:12:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan Klub Riset Hal Gaib,\Ntapi Klub Sastra Kreatif.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini aktivitas klub?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, kalian juga ikut?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.51,0:12:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biasanya begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja kami ikut!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.85,0:12:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini demi kehidupan asmara\NWakil Ketua Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.39,0:12:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanna, kau juga mau ikut, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.35,0:12:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kali pertamaku bolos sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa boleh buat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika merasakan bahaya, segera mundur.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dimengerti!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ketua Klub Riset Hal Gaib!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.78,0:12:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jauh dari sini, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.24,0:12:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau naik bus?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kubilang, ketua Klub Riset Hal Gaib…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau kembalikan detergennya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.16,0:12:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisakah sekalian kembalikan\Nkaleng minyak kosong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Merepotkan sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tak menyembunyikannya dengan baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.43,0:12:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Duh, ini sangat mengganggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.49,0:13:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kan busur dan panah\Nyang kita pakai dulu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku jadi teringat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak! Kenapa banyak senjata di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ke mana Fushi pergi?\NApa yang dia lakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.25,0:13:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini tempatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari kita sapa kakeknya dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mungkin, itu rumah musuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.51,0:13:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Musuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kedengarannya bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakeknya musuh? Ada apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Haruskah kita masuk dari sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada gerbang besi di terowongan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita bisa menghancurkannya,\Ntapi butuh waktu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.78,0:13:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini pintu masuk Kota Labirin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.95,0:13:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha mungkin ada di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itukah maksudmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saatnya Suzuhiko Senba yang cerdas masuk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:13:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan memandu menggunakan peta.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak ada sinyal internet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pintu masuk di ujung kanan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hati-hati. Licin sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kau tahu ini pintu masuknya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi terhubung dengan akarnya\Nlewat akar pohon yang tersebar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bisa merasakan arah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, dia juga tahu apa yang ada di depan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.23,0:14:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tahu tempat\Nyang bisa ditembus akar pohon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.86,0:14:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang tak bisa mereka tembus
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah jalan ke markas musuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.95,0:14:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gerbang besi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.49,0:14:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serahkan padaku, Kazumu Tamaki yang kuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.21,0:14:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lenganku sakit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamaki, kau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terbuka! Fushi memang hebat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.30,0:14:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini semua berkat Nando.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.35,0:14:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berikutnya adalah labirin asli.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:14:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua lorong mengarah ke gerbang besi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.65,0:15:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika tak membukanya,\Nkita tak akan tahu harus ke mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya giliranku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bawa harta karun yang cocok\Nuntuk memandu jalan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.03,0:15:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat! Papan Ouija.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari gunakan ini untuk tanya arah pada roh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Roh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.49,0:15:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wahai, Hantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak masalah siapa itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tolong beri tahu kami lokasi Mizuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.67,0:15:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka selalu bermain seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Bergerak!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kanan…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.09,0:15:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mungkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.80,0:15:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.01,0:15:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ke kanan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lewat sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.05,0:15:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berterima kasih kepada siapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tempat ini terbuat dari besi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin itu tempat\Nyang disebutkan Fen dan Nixon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.25,0:16:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa Mizuha ada di sana?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini cukup jauh. Kalian bisa kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa? Akhirnya kita sampai sejauh ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga ingin kalian bertemu Mizuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi satu-satunya pintu masuk
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.39,0:16:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah yang itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.85,0:16:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa Nokker\Ntakkan biarkan kalian lewat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, itu musuhnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku belum pernah melihat Nokker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menjijikkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi, hati-hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.03,0:16:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapkan tubuh cadangan untuk berjaga-jaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, kuserahkan mereka padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, aku mengandalkanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:17:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang, Fushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.07,0:17:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi, selamat menikmati.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha, Fushi datang untuk menemuimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.42,0:17:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ulang tahunmu mungkin sudah lewat,\Ntapi aku datang untuk memberimu ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Album foto?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana menurutmu? Mau melihatnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.97,0:17:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.\NBelakangan ini dia agak keras kepala.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu apa yang kau inginkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Kau menginginkan Fushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau memang hebat, Nak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:18:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha, Fushi tiada di dunia ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku di tubuh seseorang\Nyang pernah kutemui.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itukah yang kau inginkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.09,0:18:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang kau sedang bicara denganku, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.30,0:18:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nokker.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.63,0:18:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha ada di sini karena kehendakmu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dunia luar akan menyakiti Mizuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.56,0:18:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama dunia luar belum menjadi surga,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.85,0:18:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tubuh dan jiwa Mizuha\Nhanya bisa di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.11,0:18:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha, kau sungguh berpikir begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di mana hatimu yang sebenarnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua orang menunggumu kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.16,0:18:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, jika aku mati,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.42,0:18:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau akan menangis untukku?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.75,0:18:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bohong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, kau tak pernah menangis.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.67,0:18:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku… Aku pernah menangis.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudmu saat jadi penyu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu berbeda dengan situasi manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi, aku tak bisa memercayaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.94,0:19:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa pun yang kau katakan,\Ntak bisa menggerakkanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena kau siap lari kapan saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha, aku sangat iri padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah menjadi Mizuha sejak lahir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.79,0:19:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau boleh hidup sebagai Mizuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, hidup sebagai trofi Ibu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau salah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bu Izumi ingin membesarkanmu\Njadi anak kebanggaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin kau tak senang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi dia sangat menyayangimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.93,0:19:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah pasti.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.55,0:19:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu bohong. Berhenti bicara omong kosong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, kau tak bisa membuktikan\Nbahwa itu benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.81,0:19:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Album foto itu
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bisa membuktikan\Nbahwa Bu Izumi menyayangimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.28,0:20:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nokker membuat ingatan Bu Izumi bermasalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.41,0:20:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski dia sangat menderita,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.95,0:20:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ingatannya masih berpusat padamu, Mizuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.28,0:20:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia berusaha keras\Nagar tak melupakanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.26,0:20:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingat…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.18,0:20:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi, kenapa kau menunjukkan ini padaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini semua kenangan menyakitkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.56,0:20:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seharusnya kau tak melihatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, sudah waktunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.03,0:20:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Hentikan! Lepaskan aku!\N- Hentikan…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.36,0:20:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat ulang tahun, Mizuha
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.58,0:20:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat ulang tahun, Mizuha
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.87,0:20:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat ulang tahun, Mizuha
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.96,0:20:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat ulang tahun, Mizuha
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.89,0:21:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu tak sopan mengatakan ini\Ndi depan keluarga Mizuha,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.43,0:21:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi kurasa Mizuha\Ntak seharusnya di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.02,0:21:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuharap Mizuha bisa kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.19,0:21:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sedang apa kau di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sama sekali tidak peduli padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.07,0:21:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana mungkin?\NKenapa kau berkata begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.57,0:21:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau hanya bisa bicara.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.37,0:21:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah berada di sini membuktikan itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.91,0:21:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami semua bekerja sama mencarimu\Nkarena mencemaskanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.50,0:21:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanna, jangan ribut. Berisik sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berhentilah basa-basi dan katakan,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.79,0:21:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kenapa kau harus terus di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.55,0:21:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh aku menyela?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.84,0:21:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah ke dokter, Mizuha?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.05,0:21:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Belum.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.22,0:21:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anggap aku dokter dan dengarkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.76,0:21:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurang sinar matahari\Ntingkatkan risiko osteoporosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.98,0:21:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu tidak baik untuk kesehatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.69,0:21:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bukan dokter,\Njadi, aku takkan mendengarkanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.27,0:21:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.65,0:22:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha, aku tak tahu\Napa yang kau alami saat tumbuh dewasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.15,0:22:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin aku tidak bisa membantumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.78,0:22:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku ingin berusaha semampuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.24,0:22:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanna, kau tidak perlu\Nmelakukan apa pun untukku lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.95,0:22:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak menginginkan apa pun\Ndarimu sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.50,0:22:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Lantas, apa yang harus kulakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.96,0:22:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, air di sini bau busuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.04,0:22:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuenya juga tampak menjijikkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.09,0:22:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha harus pergi\Nsebelum dia ikut membusuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.80,0:22:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa yang setuju denganku?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.68,0:22:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian sudah keterlaluan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.23,0:22:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seharusnya ada batasan\Nuntuk kelancangan kalian!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.98,0:22:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat usir mereka!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.02,0:22:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa kau tak boleh\Nmelakukan itu sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.36,0:22:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.28,0:22:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi, impianmu mewujudkan\Nmimpi semua orang, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.82,0:22:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Agar impian itu terwujud,\Ndunia harus damai.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.66,0:22:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu arti kedamaian.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.88,0:24:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keanehan tiba-tiba terjadi di sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.14,0:24:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Monster mengerikan\Nmenyerang Tonari dan yang lainnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.52,0:24:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di hadapan musuh yang terus bermunculan,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.31,0:24:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apakah ada solusi?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.52,0:24:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Para gadis muda mencari kebebasan.
